com.googlecode.objectify.impl.engine

Class WriteEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.objectify.impl.engine.WriteEngine

  • public class WriteEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the master logic for loading, saving, and deleting entities from the datastore. It provides the fundamental operations that enable the rest of the API. One of these engines is created for every operation; upon completion, it is thrown away.
    Author:
    Jeff Schnitzer
